## Hugo
/public/
/resources/_gen/
.temp/
/resources/
.hugo_build.lock
hugo.exe

## OS
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
static/images/**/.*

## Local backups / exports
layouts_site_backup/

## Root dotfiles (ignore everything, except what we need)
.*
!.gitignore

## Cursor IDE — skills, rules, MCP config; keep machine-local, do not commit
# (Also covered by `.*` above; listed explicitly so .cursor/ stays out of git if `.*` is removed.)
.cursor/

## Local CI/CD vision notes (keep out of sync)
.CICD.md

## Docs that should not be pushed
/IMPLEMENTATION.md
/VISION.md

## Ignore nested git inside vendored themes
themes/**/.git/
